title: #looflife - Loofgram
description:
#looflife is a video created by Adam Akins. The meaning of loof life is based around street skating, with the objective of raw fun. Primarily featuring the Uprise Skateshop crew out of Chicago, this vid also has a heavy dose of Parisian "euro loof famille".
Check out the hashtag "#looflife" on Instagram
